'''2015年孟買甲醇中毒事件'''，是指發生於2015年6月17日，在[[印度|印度]][[孟買|孟買]]{{link-en|孟買西郊區|Western Suburbs (Mumbai)|西郊}}北部{{link-en|馬拉德 (孟買)|Malad|馬拉德}}的拉克什米·納加（Laxmi Nagar）[[貧民窟|貧民窟]]的一起集體[[中毒|中毒]]事件。有部分人飲用了私釀的假酒後病倒<ref name=latimes>{{cite web | url=http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-toxic-hooch-in-india-leaves-84-dead-20150620-story.html | title=84 dead in India after drinking toxic homemade liquor | work=Los Angeles Times | date=20 June 2015 | accessdate=21 June 2015 | author=Bengali, Shashank | archive-date=2015-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622004913/http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-toxic-hooch-in-india-leaves-84-dead-20150620-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，截至6月20日統計，至少有90人已經因此死亡<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-33179175 | title=India toxic alcohol kills 84 in Mumbai | work=BBC News | date=20 June 2015 | accessdate=20 June 2015 | archive-date=2015-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622132357/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-33179175 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="aljazeera">{{cite web | url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/06/toxic-alcohol-kills-scores-india-mumbai-150620131103400.html | title=Toxic alcohol kills scores in India's Mumbai | work=Al Jazeera | date=20 June 2015 | accessdate=20 June 2015 | archive-date=2015-06-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621053501/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/06/toxic-alcohol-kills-scores-india-mumbai-150620131103400.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，另外31人住院治療<ref>{{cite web | url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/tainted-liquor-kills-84-indias-financial-hub-mumbai-31908466 | title=Tainted Liquor Kills 84 in India's Financial Hub of Mumbai | work=ABC News | date=20 June 2015 | accessdate=20 June 2015 | archive-date=2015-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620131741/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/tainted-liquor-kills-84-indias-financial-hub-mumbai-31908466 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。本次事件是當地近十年來最慘重的集體酒精中毒事件，死亡人數預計還要再增加<ref name=nytimes>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/21/world/asia/toxic-liquor-in-india-kills-at-least-84.html?_r=0 | title=Toxic Liquor in India Kills at Least 84 | work=New York Times | date=20 June 2015 | accessdate=20 June 2015 | author=Najar, Nida | archive-date=2015-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620202343/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/21/world/asia/toxic-liquor-in-india-kills-at-least-84.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
在印度，飲用劣質[[私酒|私酒]]或假酒，而導致集體中毒的事件時常發生，因為窮人往往買不起有{{link-en|販酒執照|Liquor license}}商店的酒。2004年，鄰近孟買的{{link-en|維克羅利|Vikhroli}}就曾發生同類事件，致使104人死亡<ref name=aljazeera />。
== 逮捕 ==
5名與本起事件有關的嫌犯已被[[逮捕|逮捕]]，而8名當地[[警察|警察]]也因沒有積極查緝，怠忽職守，受到停職處分<ref name=nytimes/>；此外，協助運輸與銷售假酒的工人也一併被捕<ref name=aljazeera/>。

== 原因 ==
據警方透露，受害者是因為喝下了含有[[甲醇|甲醇]]的酒導致中毒<ref name=latimes />。

